The paper deals with Reinforcement Learning (RL) and robotics, which are both subfields of computer science. The focus of the paper is on a novel technique called Hindsight Experience Replay, which is a form of implicit curriculum for RL algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
